# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible. The remote deploy ships
# a `git archive` (tracked files only), but a local `docker compose build` uses
# the full working tree - exclude build output, dependencies, and VCS so the
# context stays lean and stale artifacts never leak into an image.
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.vs/
.git/
.github/
*.tar
**/*.user
.env
